race.comment: SKY BLUE (8) has been thereabouts in all three Toowoomba runs this campaign and will be ready to peak now at the fourth run back. Gets Maloney on top and can run a big race despite the wide draw. RYLOV (1) has won two from four when second-up and gets some weight relief with the 3kg claim. Strips fitter now and rates a definite top-three conveyance. DARLING TAKE CARE (7) finally got the maiden out of the way at the latest outing and Thornton stays in the stirrups. Keep very safe with that victory now under the belt. THE IMMORTALS (4) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be underestimated with Lerena staying on board.
